<item>
            <title>[LU-4700] Help on Multirail configuration for Dual HCA OSS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4700</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi List,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please suggest for the multi-rail configuration with OSS, since i got confused with multiple types of configurations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My setup as follows..&lt;br/&gt;
1. MDS server1 - 192.168.1.40@o2ib&lt;br/&gt;
2. MDS server2 - 192.168.1.42@o2ib&lt;br/&gt;
3. OSS server1 - 192.168.1.44@o2ib, 192.168.1.45@o2ib1&lt;br/&gt;
4. OSS server2 - 192.168.1.46@o2ib, 192.168.1.47@o2ib1&lt;br/&gt;
5. Clients - 192.168.1.50-57@o2ib&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MDS and cleints has only single port HCAs and OSS servers has two HCAs. I&apos;m not able to ping the o2ib1 network from any of the MDS/clients, since they are into o2ib network. I&apos;m not interested to make a separate fabric for only two interfaces in oss. Please suggest.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
